name: 85-Year Tenure Ring
description: A small token awarded by the BEE.E.O. to those who dedicate their entire lives to service.

spells.description: Equip: Your attacks have a chance to harmonize with the shard, granting you 14,839 Agility for 15 sec.

Use: Raise your signet to the Light, increasing your highest secondary stat by 6,681 for 20 sec. Your act inspires nearby signetbearers within your party, granting them 176 of the same stat for 20 sec. (2 Min Cooldown)
Equip: Don the mantle of the Trashmaster.

Equip: Your damaging spells and abilities have a chance to siphon 196,124 Health from yourself and cast it into the void for 3 seconds. 

Upon its return, deal 424,979 damage to a random enemy within 30 yards.

This is a Nerubian embellishment.
